commentary: McKay to Salman Butt, OUT Asoka has struck again, no movement, going with angle, headed towards middle stump, and it had to be pitched outside leg. Asoka de Silva doesn't think so, and raises his finger. It's pitched way outside leg. What's more? It's going over the stumps. Salman Butt is furious as he walks off. No show of dissent at the wicket, though
